commit.message:
* gcc.dg/weak-1.c: Fix scan tests.

From-SVN: r50821

files.patch:
@@ -1,3 +1,7 @@
+2002-03-15  Richard Earnshaw  <rearnsha@arm.com>
+
+	* gcc.dg/weak-1.c: Fix scan tests.
+
 2002-03-15  Hans-Peter Nilsson  <hp@bitrange.com>
 
 	* gcc.dg/20020312-2.c [__MMIX__]: No pic register.

@@ -2,14 +2,14 @@
 /* COFF does not support weak, and dg doesn't support UNSUPPORTED.  */
 /* { dg-do compile { xfail *-*-coff i?86-pc-cygwin } } */
 
-/* { dg-final { scan-assembler "weak[^ 	]*[ 	]_?a" } } */
-/* { dg-final { scan-assembler "weak[^ 	]*[ 	]_?b" } } */
-/* { dg-final { scan-assembler "weak[^ 	]*[ 	]_?c" } } */
-/* { dg-final { scan-assembler "weak[^ 	]*[ 	]_?d" } } */
-/* { dg-final { scan-assembler "weak[^ 	]*[ 	]_?e" } } */
-/* { dg-final { scan-assembler "weak[^ 	]*[ 	]_?g" } } */
-/* { dg-final { scan-assembler-not "weak[^ 	]*[ 	]_?i" } } */
-/* { dg-final { scan-assembler "weak[^ 	]*[ 	]_?j" } } */
+/* { dg-final { scan-assembler "weak\[^ \t\]*\[ \t]_?a" } } */
+/* { dg-final { scan-assembler "weak\[^ \t\]*\[ \t]_?b" } } */
+/* { dg-final { scan-assembler "weak\[^ \t\]*\[ \t]_?c" } } */
+/* { dg-final { scan-assembler "weak\[^ \t\]*\[ \t]_?d" } } */
+/* { dg-final { scan-assembler "weak\[^ \t\]*\[ \t]_?e" } } */
+/* { dg-final { scan-assembler "weak\[^ \t\]*\[ \t]_?g" } } */
+/* { dg-final { scan-assembler-not "weak\[^ \t\]*\[ \t]_?i" } } */
+/* { dg-final { scan-assembler "weak\[^ \t\]*\[ \t]_?j" } } */
 
 #pragma weak a
 int a;
